ggstatsplot in R

Wyclife Agumba Oluoch (wyclifeoluoch@gmail.com)

2022-02-27 09:44:40

Background

In this short tutorial, I am going to show the usage of ggstatsplot for embedding statistical values on ggplot graphics.

ggbetweenstats

ggbetweenstats(data = movies_long, x = mpaa, y = rating)

The plot can also be improved to give more information such as:

ggbetweenstats(data = movies_long, x = mpaa, y = rating,
               type = 'np', pairwise.display = 'ns')

or

ggbetweenstats(data = movies_long, 
               x = mpaa, 
               y = rating,
               type = 'r', 
               pairwise.comparisons = FALSE,
               outlier.tagging = TRUE,
               outlier.label = title)

ggwithinstats

Same can also be done for the ggwithinstats as follows:

ggwithinstats(data = WRS2::WineTasting, Wine, Taste)

gghistostats

gghistostats(data = movies_long, x = budget, test.value = 30)

ggdotplotstats

ggdotplotstats(movies_long,
               budget, genre, test.value = 30)

ggscatterstats

ggscatterstats(movies_long, budget, rating,
               type = 'r',
               label.var = title, 
               label.expression = budget > 150 & rating > 7.5)

ggpiestats

ggpiestats(
  data         = mtcars,
  x            = am,
  y            = cyl,
  package      = "wesanderson",
  palette      = "Royal1",
  title        = "Dataset: Motor Trend Car Road Tests", ## title for the plot
  legend.title = "Transmission", ## title for the legend
  caption      = "Source: 1974 Motor Trend US magazine"
)

ggbarstats

ggbarstats(
  data             = movies_long,
  x                = mpaa,
  y                = genre,
  title            = "MPAA Ratings by Genre",
  xlab             = "movie genre",
  legend.title     = "MPAA rating",
  ggtheme          = hrbrthemes::theme_ipsum_pub(),
  ggplot.component = list(ggplot2::scale_x_discrete(guide = ggplot2::guide_axis(n.dodge = 2))),
  palette          = "Set2"
)

ggcoefstats

mod <- lm(rating~mpaa, data = movies_long)
ggcoefstats(mod)

grouped_ggpiestats

grouped_ggpiestats(mtcars, x = cyl, grouping.var = am)

ggbetweenstats customized

ggbetweenstats(movies_long,
               mpaa, rating, 
              ggtheme = hrbrthemes::theme_ipsum_tw(),
              palettete = "Darjeeling2")
